Class IncrementalLearningSkeleton.Predictor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.examples.ml.IncrementalLearningSkeleton.Predictor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Function, CoMapFunction<Integer,Double[],Integer>
    Enclosing class:
    IncrementalLearningSkeleton

    public static class IncrementalLearningSkeleton.Predictor
extends Object
implements CoMapFunction<Integer,Double[],Integer>
    Creates prediction using the model produced in batch-processing and the up-to-date partial model.

    By defaults emits the Integer 0 for every prediction and the Integer 1 for every model update.
